beginning, containing an area of ONE HUNDRED EIGHTY THOUSAND (180,000) square meters. All points referred to are indicated on the plan and are marked on the ground by P.S. cyl. conc. mons. 15 x 40 cms. Bearings true, date of original survey, March 1915-April 1916, and that of the subdivision survey: April 1 – May 4, 1978 and was approved on June 13, 1978.

The land hereinabove described shall be exclusively utilized as site of Regional Offices of the National Government Agencies in Region III and lot allocation of each agency shall be based on the approved Disposition Guidelines to be formulated by the Inter-Agency Task Force under the Regional Development Council Sectoral Committee on Development Administration.

The RDC III is hereby authorized to administer the property to ensure its proper use in coordination with other national government agencies based in Region III.

IN WITNESS WHEREOF, I have hereunto set my hand and caused the seal of the Republic of the Philippines to be affixed.

Done in the City of Manila, this 17 Th day of July, in the year of Our Lord, two thousand.

(Sgd.) JOSEPH EJERCITO ESTRADA

By the President: RONALDO B. ZAMORA Executive Secretary

